<li id="cite_note-80"><b><a href="#cite_ref-80" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.populationconnection.org/About_Us/policies.html" class="external text" title="http://www.populationconnection.org/About_Us/policies.html" rel="nofollow">Population Connection</a> Statement of Policy</li>
